Description: Code repository for Satterthwaite et al., "Microbial and small
    zooplankton communities predict density of baleen whales in the southern
    California Current Ecosystem." Implements a sparse PLS stability selection
    pipeline to identify eDNA features predictive of baleen whale density, and
    provides vignettes demonstrating the methodology on example data.
